  <brief_title>Optimized Caloric-proteic Nutrition in Septic and Septic Shock Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Impact of Optimized Caloric-proteic Nutrition on Clinical Outcome and Physical Component Summary (PCS) of Quality of Life in Septic and Septic Shock Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
