  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients admitted to the ICU with sepsis and septic shock according to 3rd
             International Sepsis Consensus Conference Definitions for sepsis and septic shock

          -  Mechanically ventilated

          -  Expected length of stay in ICU ≥ 4 days

          -  Written informed consent obtained from authorized surrogates

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Requirement for inspired oxygen content (FIO2) &gt; 0.60

          -  High output bronchopleural fistula
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
